Dialogue: 1,0:01:02.81,0:01:04.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,收获我作物
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.81,0:01:04.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Harvesting my crops
Dialogue: 1,0:01:04.36,0:01:05.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,呀塔塔塔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.36,0:01:05.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ya-ta-ta-ta
Dialogue: 1,0:01:05.81,0:01:07.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,辣椒品相好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.81,0:01:07.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Peppers look delish
Dialogue: 1,0:01:07.17,0:01:08.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,呀塔塔塔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.17,0:01:08.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ya-ta-ta-ta
Dialogue: 1,0:01:08.75,0:01:10.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,香蕉椒也是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.75,0:01:10.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Banana peppers too
Dialogue: 1,0:01:10.57,0:01:11.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,呀塔塔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.57,0:01:11.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ya-ta-ta
Dialogue: 1,0:01:11.62,0:01:12.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,塔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.62,0:01:12.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ta
Dialogue: 1,0:01:14.92,0:01:16.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早安  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.92,0:01:16.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:01:16.52,0:01:17.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,呀塔塔塔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.52,0:01:17.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ya-ta-ta-ta
Dialogue: 1,0:01:17.65,0:01:19.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,呀塔塔塔个屁
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.65,0:01:19.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ya-ta-ta-ta my foot
Dialogue: 1,0:01:19.72,0:01:20.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你害我把墨
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.72,0:01:20.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You made me ink
Dialogue: 1,0:01:20.73,0:01:22.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,喷到我最后一件干净衬衣上了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.73,0:01:22.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,on my last clean shirt
Dialogue: 1,0:01:22.67,0:01:25.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在不得不去自助洗衣店了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.67,0:01:25.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now I have to go to the laundromat
Dialogue: 1,0:01:29.52,0:01:30.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,自助洗衣店吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.52,0:01:30.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The laundromat?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:30.97,0:01:32.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那可是个神奇的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.97,0:01:32.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why, that's a magical place
Dialogue: 1,0:01:32.85,0:01:35.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以把所有污垢和灰尘都洗掉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.85,0:01:35.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,where all filth and grime is washed away
Dialogue: 1,0:01:35.80,0:01:37.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让衣服焕然一新
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.80,0:01:37.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,making clothes spring fresh
Dialogue: 1,0:01:39.84,0:01:42.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我家里有不少脏衣服得洗一下烘一下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.84,0:01:42.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I have a lot of filthy clothes that need a spin and dry
Dialogue: 1,0:01:42.85,0:01:44.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我也要去洗衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.85,0:01:44.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll do my laundry too
Dialogue: 1,0:01:44.67,0:01:46.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等我一下  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.67,0:01:46.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait for me, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:01:46.17,0:01:48.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就在这等
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.17,0:01:48.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll wait right here
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.13,0:01:56.22,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(702,434)}洗刷刷
Dialogue: 1,0:02:02.54,0:02:03.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.54,0:02:03.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:02:05.01,0:02:06.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.01,0:02:06.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait for me
Dialogue: 1,0:02:07.31,0:02:09.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,慢点  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.31,0:02:09.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Slow down, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:02:16.05,0:02:19.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全裤头村的人今天都来洗衣服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.05,0:02:19.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is everyone in town doing their laundry today?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:20.48,0:02:23.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早知道就凌晨两点没人的时候过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.48,0:02:23.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I should've come at 2 a.m. when it's empty
Dialogue: 1,0:02:23.11,0:02:26.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可那样就没法认识我的臭袜朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.11,0:02:26.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But then you wouldn't get to meet my stinky sock friend
Dialogue: 1,0:02:26.25,0:02:27.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,臭袜朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.25,0:02:27.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stinky sock friend?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:27.69,0:02:29.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你到底在扯什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.69,0:02:29.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What in the world are you talking about?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:34.50,0:02:35.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,认真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.50,0:02:35.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:39.00,0:02:40.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有个空的洗衣机
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.00,0:02:40.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,An open machine
Dialogue: 1,0:02:48.53,0:02:51.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢你帮我占洗衣机  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.53,0:02:51.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks for holding the washer for me, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:02:51.41,0:02:53.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  你没穿衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.41,0:02:53.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, you're naked
Dialogue: 1,0:02:53.84,0:02:55.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那我就需要这个
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.84,0:02:55.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then I'm gonna need this
Dialogue: 1,0:02:55.84,0:02:56.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快还我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.84,0:02:56.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Give me that
Dialogue: 1,0:02:57.60,0:02:58.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,改穿这个
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.60,0:02:58.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Take this instead
Dialogue: 1,0:02:59.49,0:03:00.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.49,0:03:00.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:03:00.81,0:03:03.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我竟能有这般荣幸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.81,0:03:03.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't believe I've had the pleasure
Dialogue: 1,0:03:03.16,0:03:04.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好笨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.16,0:03:04.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're so silly
Dialogue: 1,0:03:12.67,0:03:15.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好强的臭味
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.67,0:03:15.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That is one strong stink
Dialogue: 1,0:03:17.31,0:03:19.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好啊  比就比
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.31,0:03:19.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, let's do this
Dialogue: 1,0:03:21.59,0:03:24.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早知道就喷点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.59,0:03:24.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe I should have worn
Dialogue: 1,0:03:24.24,0:03:25.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,除臭剂了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.24,0:03:25.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,deodorant
Dialogue: 1,0:03:28.12,0:03:29.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我能借用一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.12,0:03:29.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can I borrow this a sec?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:29.75,0:03:30.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.75,0:03:30.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks
Dialogue: 1,0:03:30.40,0:03:31.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.40,0:03:31.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:03:31.53,0:03:33.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我才是下一个排队的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.53,0:03:33.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm next in line
Dialogue: 1,0:03:33.15,0:03:34.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别插队
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.15,0:03:34.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No cut-sies
Dialogue: 1,0:03:34.80,0:03:36.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不需要洗衣机  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.80,0:03:36.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't need a machine, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:03:36.31,0:03:37.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只要一点肥皂就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.31,0:03:37.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I just need a little soap
Dialogue: 1,0:03:55.75,0:03:57.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,干净得不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.75,0:03:57.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Clean as a hog-whistle
Dialogue: 1,0:03:58.02,0:03:59.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.02,0:03:59.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So long, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:04:04.39,0:04:07.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小猪猪  该来洗澡了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.39,0:04:07.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, little piggy, time for a bath
Dialogue: 1,0:04:19.37,0:04:21.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,麻烦结账
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.37,0:04:21.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Check please
Dialogue: 1,0:04:21.21,0:04:23.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太神了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.21,0:04:23.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Amazing
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.53,0:04:23.03,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(568,466)}太神了
Dialogue: 1,0:04:27.75,0:04:29.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太神了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.75,0:04:29.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Amazing
Dialogue: 1,0:04:30.82,0:04:31.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太神
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.82,0:04:31.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ama
Dialogue: 1,0:04:31.65,0:04:32.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.65,0:04:32.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Zing
Dialogue: 1,0:04:37.12,0:04:39.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太香了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.12,0:04:39.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mmm-mazing
Dialogue: 1,0:04:50.37,0:04:51.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我都忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.37,0:04:51.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I forgot
Dialogue: 1,0:04:51.45,0:04:54.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的皮肤只能干洗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.45,0:04:54.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My skin is dry clean only
Dialogue: 1,0:04:56.48,0:04:59.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,总算要来洗掉这污渍了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.48,0:04:59.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Finally, time to extract this stain
Dialogue: 1,0:04:59.57,0:05:01.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你手上那是什么  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.57,0:05:01.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Whatcha got there, Squidward?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:01.94,0:05:04.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以去除烦人的污渍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.94,0:05:04.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It removes annoying stains
Dialogue: 1,0:05:04.73,0:05:06.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但不幸的是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.73,0:05:06.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately for me
Dialogue: 1,0:05:06.08,0:05:08.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它没法去除烦人的海绵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.08,0:05:08.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,it doesn't remove annoying sponges
Dialogue: 1,0:05:29.08,0:05:31.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,洗掉吧  这该死的污点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.08,0:05:31.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Out, darn spot
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.08,0:05:31.27,注释,,0,0,0,,[ 引自莎士比亚《麦克白》 ]
Dialogue: 1,0:05:37.49,0:05:39.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,污渍不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.49,0:05:39.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The stain is gone
Dialogue: 1,0:05:40.17,0:05:42.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你穿上去的样子真帅气
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.17,0:05:42.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That looks marvelous on you
Dialogue: 1,0:05:42.27,0:05:43.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来看看背面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.27,0:05:43.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's see the back
Dialogue: 1,0:05:46.57,0:05:47.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.57,0:05:47.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:47.52,0:05:48.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你得来件更大的衬衣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.52,0:05:48.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're gonna need a bigger shirt
Dialogue: 1,0:05:50.81,0:05:51.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.81,0:05:51.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What the?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:54.05,0:05:56.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真希望我能帮上忙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.05,0:05:56.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I wish there was something I could do to help
Dialogue: 1,0:05:59.95,0:06:01.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.95,0:06:01.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait a second
Dialogue: 1,0:06:06.54,0:06:08.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,用力点搓  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.54,0:06:08.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Scrub harder, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:06:12.72,0:06:16.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,感觉你清理实验器材的方式不正规
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.72,0:06:14.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Seems like an unorthodox way
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.81,0:06:16.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,of cleaning your lab equipment
Dialogue: 1,0:06:16.67,0:06:18.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,少挖苦我了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.67,0:06:18.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stop busting my antenna
Dialogue: 1,0:06:18.73,0:06:21.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样子更快  而且只要两毛五
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.73,0:06:21.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is quicker and it only costs a quarter
Dialogue: 1,0:06:25.40,0:06:27.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,多半是器材放得不均匀导致的振动
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.40,0:06:27.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's an unbalanced load
Dialogue: 1,0:06:27.60,0:06:29.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也有可能是你忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.60,0:06:29.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Or maybe you forgot
Dialogue: 1,0:06:29.52,0:06:33.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给试管上面的变异配方冲干净
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.52,0:06:33.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to rinse those mutation formulas off those test tubes
Dialogue: 1,0:06:56.63,0:06:57.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,妈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.63,0:06:57.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mommy
Dialogue: 1,0:06:58.80,0:07:01.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,事情老被你说中  你就不觉得烦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.80,0:07:01.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't you ever get tired of being right?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:30.12,0:07:31.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的裤腿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.12,0:07:31.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My pant leg
Dialogue: 1,0:07:53.34,0:07:55.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蒂  乖一点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.34,0:07:55.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tilly, be nice
Dialogue: 1,0:07:55.15,0:07:57.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别去咬那个上过浆的衬衣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.15,0:07:57.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Leave that starched shirt alone
Dialogue: 1,0:08:22.52,0:08:23.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.52,0:08:23.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It worked
Dialogue: 1,0:08:23.60,0:08:25.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,墨渍洗掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.60,0:08:25.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The ink spot is gone
Dialogue: 1,0:08:25.17,0:08:26.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就知道你能行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.17,0:08:26.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I knew you could do it
Dialogue: 1,0:08:28.32,0:08:29.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.32,0:08:29.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:08:29.55,0:08:30.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.55,0:08:30.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh no
Dialogue: 1,0:08:30.43,0:08:32.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,墨渍跑我背心去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.43,0:08:32.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The spot is on my undershirt
Dialogue: 1,0:08:53.51,0:08:54.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.51,0:08:54.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:08:55.16,0:08:56.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.16,0:08:56.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:57.22,0:08:59.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好办法  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.22,0:08:59.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good idea, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:08:59.43,0:09:03.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就用这淀粉浆彻底定住那滩墨渍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.43,0:09:01.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll hold that spot in place
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.31,0:09:03.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,once and for all with this starch
Dialogue: 1,0:09:04.48,0:09:06.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,说晚安吧  墨渍
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.48,0:09:06.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Say goodnight, Spot
Dialogue: 1,0:09:34.31,0:09:36.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,洗衣机死掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.31,0:09:36.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The washing machine is dead
Dialogue: 1,0:09:36.47,0:09:39.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的衣服又干净到能发光
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.47,0:09:39.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And my clothes are sparkling clean
Dialogue: 1,0:09:46.02,0:09:47.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,完事了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.02,0:09:47.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Welp, that's done
Dialogue: 1,0:09:48.41,0:09:50.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,回去打理我的秋海棠
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.41,0:09:50.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Back to my begonias
Dialogue: 1,0:09:50.27,0:09:51.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他除掉了怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.27,0:09:51.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He killed the monster
Dialogue: 1,0:09:51.66,0:09:53.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他救了我们的命
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.66,0:09:53.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He saved our lives
Dialogue: 1,0:09:53.30,0:09:55.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他是我们的英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.30,0:09:55.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's our hero
Dialogue: 1,0:09:55.57,0:09:56.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没没没
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.57,0:09:56.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, no, no, no
Dialogue: 1,0:09:56.43,0:09:58.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我什么都没干啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.43,0:09:58.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I didn't do anything
Dialogue: 1,0:09:58.06,0:09:59.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我什么人都没救
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.06,0:09:59.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I didn't save anyone
Dialogue: 1,0:09:59.80,0:10:01.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你也是我的英雄  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.80,0:10:01.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're my hero too, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:10:04.21,0:10:07.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.21,0:10:07.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:10:07.86,0:10:09.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我只想回家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.86,0:10:09.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I just wanna go home
Dialogue: 1,0:10:12.20,0:10:14.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想今天大家都学到了一课
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.20,0:10:14.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think we all learned a lesson here today
Dialogue: 1,0:10:14.94,0:10:16.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而我对此写了一首歌
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.94,0:10:16.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and I wrote a song about it
Dialogue: 1,0:10:16.89,0:10:19.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它是这么唱的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.89,0:10:19.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It goes a little something like this
Dialogue: 1,0:10:20.10,0:10:20.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.10,0:10:20.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hit it
Dialogue: 1,0:10:21.23,0:10:22.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,洗衣烘干
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.23,0:10:22.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wash and dry
Dialogue: 1,0:10:22.54,0:10:23.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的天
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.54,0:10:23.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My oh my
Dialogue: 1,0:10:23.60,0:10:25.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,肥皂泡沫进我眼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.60,0:10:25.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got soapsuds in my eye
Dialogue: 1,0:10:25.65,0:10:26.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,袜子飞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.65,0:10:26.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Socks will fly
Dialogue: 1,0:10:26.82,0:10:27.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,污渍灭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.82,0:10:27.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stains will die
Dialogue: 1,0:10:27.82,0:10:30.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家一起来烘干
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.82,0:10:30.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Everybody Tumble Dry
Dialogue: 1,0:10:30.96,0:10:32.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,裙子净
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.96,0:10:32.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Skirts are clean
Dialogue: 1,0:10:32.24,0:10:33.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,裤子蒸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.24,0:10:33.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pants are steamed
Dialogue: 1,0:10:33.25,0:10:35.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拿出机器正新鲜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.25,0:10:35.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fresh out of the dang machine
Dialogue: 1,0:10:35.23,0:10:36.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,漂白衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.23,0:10:36.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bleach your clothes
Dialogue: 1,0:10:36.48,0:10:37.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,泡紧身裤
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.48,0:10:37.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Soak your hose
Dialogue: 1,0:10:37.57,0:10:39.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,洗衣就是这么办
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.57,0:10:39.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is how a washer goes
Dialogue: 1,0:10:39.70,0:10:41.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,咕噜转转拉咔咔咔嘎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.70,0:10:41.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Glug Glug, Spin Spin Ra-Kakakaka Glug
Dialogue: 1,0:10:41.86,0:10:43.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,咕噜转转拉咔咔咔咔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.86,0:10:43.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Glug Glug, Spin Spin Ra-Kakakaka
Dialogue: 1,0:10:45.06,0:10:47.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,洗衣烘干我不骗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.06,0:10:47.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wash and Dry, I won't lie
Dialogue: 1,0:10:47.27,0:10:49.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我等不及说再见
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.27,0:10:49.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't wait to say goodbye
Dialogue: 1,0:10:49.37,0:10:51.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,咕噜转转拜拜拜拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.37,0:10:51.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Glug Glug, Spin Spin Bye-Bubububye
Dialogue: 1,0:10:51.56,0:10:53.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,咕噜转转拜拜拜拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.56,0:10:53.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Glug Glug, Spin Spin Bye-Bubububye
Dialogue: 1,0:10:53.34,0:10:55.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.34,0:10:55.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, wait for me
Dialogue: 1,0:11:03.16,0:11:05.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拜拜拜拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.16,0:11:05.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bye-Bubububye
Dialogue: 1,0:11:21.94,0:11:23.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只是墨水而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.94,0:11:23.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's just ink
Dialogue: 1,0:11:23.60,0:11:24.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我会清理掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.60,0:11:24.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll clean it up
Dialogue: 1,0:11:31.29,0:11:33.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想见见我的小猪猪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.29,0:11:33.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Would you like to meet my piggy?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.21,0:11:38.80,起司 一般标题,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}捉猪大作战
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.01,0:11:40.17,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(750,408)}编剧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.01,0:11:40.17,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(768,700)}分镜总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.01,0:11:44.64,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1530,976.667)}翻译{\fnArial}: 1440kHz
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.47,0:11:41.63,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(636,484)}指导总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.47,0:11:41.63,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(800,700)}动画总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.93,0:11:43.09,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(740,548)}统筹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.39,0:11:44.55,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(596,560)}监制
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.85,0:11:46.26,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(640,598)}监制
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.85,0:11:46.26,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1468.667,976.667)}本字幕仅限学习交流\N严禁用于商业用途
Dialogue: 1,0:11:49.99,0:11:52.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在送外卖
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.99,0:11:52.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm delivering
Dialogue: 1,0:11:52.35,0:11:54.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在送外卖  我在送外卖
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.35,0:11:54.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm delivering, I'm delivering
Dialogue: 1,0:11:54.75,0:11:56.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在送外卖
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.75,0:11:56.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm delivering
Dialogue: 1,0:11:59.17,0:12:02.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,滚出我家门廊  政府官员
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.17,0:12:02.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Off my porch, government man
Dialogue: 1,0:12:02.00,0:12:04.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不然我就把你戳得浑身是洞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.00,0:12:04.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Or I'll poke you full of holes
Dialogue: 1,0:12:04.33,0:12:05.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别戳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.33,0:12:05.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't poke
Dialogue: 1,0:12:05.40,0:12:07.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我身上已经有洞了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.40,0:12:07.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I already have holes
Dialogue: 1,0:12:07.34,0:12:08.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,表明你的来意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.34,0:12:08.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,State your business
Dialogue: 1,0:12:08.95,0:12:11.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹堡王外卖
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.95,0:12:11.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Food delivery from the Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:12:14.13,0:12:16.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给你  尊贵的客人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.13,0:12:16.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here you go, valued customer
Dialogue: 1,0:12:20.55,0:12:23.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来情况属实
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.55,0:12:23.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I reckon that checks out
Dialogue: 1,0:12:23.60,0:12:25.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来看看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.60,0:12:25.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's see here
Dialogue: 1,0:12:26.64,0:12:30.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你到底是在耍什么花招
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.64,0:12:30.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What in tarnation are ya trying to pull here
Dialogue: 1,0:12:30.22,0:12:31.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你个骗人精
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.22,0:12:31.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,ya skilamalink
Dialogue: 1,0:12:31.87,0:12:34.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有什么问题吗  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.87,0:12:34.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is there something wrong, sir?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:34.48,0:12:37.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你少给了我的免费餐巾纸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.48,0:12:37.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You cheated me out of my free napkin
Dialogue: 1,0:12:37.90,0:12:39.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我明明带了餐巾纸  还放进了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.90,0:12:39.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I thought I grabbed napkins and put 'em in the
Dialogue: 1,0:12:39.95,0:12:40.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,袋子里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.95,0:12:40.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,bag
Dialogue: 1,0:12:40.65,0:12:43.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你害我没得选
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.65,0:12:43.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You leave me no choice
Dialogue: 1,0:12:43.49,0:12:44.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.49,0:12:44.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna
Dialogue: 1,0:12:45.05,0:12:46.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.05,0:12:46.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna
Dialogue: 1,0:12:47.23,0:12:49.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,写封长长的泄愤信
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.23,0:12:49.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,write a long angry letter
Dialogue: 1,0:12:50.30,0:12:51.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你在这等着
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.30,0:12:51.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You wait here
Dialogue: 1,0:12:51.50,0:12:56.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不准用你肮脏的城市居民手碰我东西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.50,0:12:53.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and don't touch my things
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.41,0:12:56.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,with yer filthy city-dweller hands
Dialogue: 1,0:12:58.51,0:13:01.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,边等边到处看看没什么问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.51,0:13:01.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I guess there's no harm in looking around while I wait
Dialogue: 1,0:13:01.64,0:13:04.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只要管好自己的手就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.64,0:13:04.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,As long as I keep my hands to myself
Dialogue: 1,0:13:09.22,0:13:10.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有个谷仓
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.22,0:13:10.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A barn
Dialogue: 1,0:13:12.40,0:13:13.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那是什么声音
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.40,0:13:13.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's that noise?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:14.57,0:13:17.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,获奖虫猪  禁止入内
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.57,0:13:17.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Prize worm-hog, stay out"
Dialogue: 1,0:13:17.80,0:13:19.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,幸好我不是获奖虫猪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.80,0:13:19.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good thing I'm not a prize worm-hog
Dialogue: 1,0:13:21.12,0:13:24.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的城市居民手差点就碰到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.12,0:13:24.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I almost touched it with my filthy city-dweller hands
Dialogue: 1,0:13:24.29,0:13:26.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过老头简金斯可没有说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.29,0:13:26.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But Old Man Jenkins didn't say anything
Dialogue: 1,0:13:26.23,0:13:28.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我超干净的脚不能碰
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.23,0:13:28.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,about my super clean feet
Dialogue: 1,0:13:37.01,0:13:38.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.01,0:13:38.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Excuse me?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:39.47,0:13:41.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.47,0:13:41.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:13:41.17,0:13:41.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.17,0:13:41.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:41.99,0:13:43.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你在这干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.99,0:13:43.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:43.41,0:13:47.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在帮老头简金斯给获奖虫猪做准备
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.41,0:13:47.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm helping Old Man Jenkins get his prize worm-hog ready
Dialogue: 1,0:13:47.98,0:13:49.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,去参加县集市
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.98,0:13:49.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for the county fair
Dialogue: 1,0:13:49.65,0:13:51.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看看这地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.65,0:13:51.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Check this place out
Dialogue: 1,0:13:51.69,0:13:53.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有这玩意
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.69,0:13:53.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's this stuff
Dialogue: 1,0:14:00.18,0:14:02.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有个梳妆台
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.18,0:14:02.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's a makeup station
Dialogue: 1,0:14:08.89,0:14:11.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这些美照拍的是获奖虫猪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.89,0:14:10.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is that the prize worm-hog
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.24,0:14:11.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,in all these beautiful pictures?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:11.95,0:14:14.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  它的名字叫碧拉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.95,0:14:14.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, her name is Beulah
Dialogue: 1,0:14:15.05,0:14:16.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好可爱的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.05,0:14:16.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What a lovely name
Dialogue: 1,0:14:16.80,0:14:18.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这些都是你负责做的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.80,0:14:18.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And you're in charge of all this?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:19.19,0:14:22.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没  我只负责给泥巴保暖
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.19,0:14:22.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, I just keep the mud warm
Dialogue: 1,0:14:24.90,0:14:26.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,特别暖
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.90,0:14:26.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Really warm
Dialogue: 1,0:14:26.38,0:14:27.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,碧拉在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.38,0:14:27.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where's Beulah?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:27.63,0:14:31.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它在美美的枕头上美美地睡午觉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.63,0:14:31.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,She's fancy napping on her fancy pillows
Dialogue: 1,0:14:31.43,0:14:32.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉跟你说一下  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.43,0:14:32.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I hate to tell you, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:14:32.96,0:14:34.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它不在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.96,0:14:34.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but she's not there
Dialogue: 1,0:14:35.20,0:14:36.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.20,0:14:36.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,She's gone
Dialogue: 1,0:14:36.29,0:14:36.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.29,0:14:36.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look
Dialogue: 1,0:14:36.68,0:14:38.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它的围栏开着
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.68,0:14:38.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Her pen is open
Dialogue: 1,0:14:38.69,0:14:41.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大门也开着
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.69,0:14:41.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And so's the front door
Dialogue: 1,0:14:43.02,0:14:45.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老头简金斯一定会特别生气
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.02,0:14:45.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Old Man Jenkins is gonna be so mad
Dialogue: 1,0:14:45.98,0:14:49.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他会把我给戳得浑身是洞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.98,0:14:49.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's gonna poke me full of holes
Dialogue: 1,0:14:49.33,0:14:52.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我长长的泄愤信写完了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.33,0:14:52.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I finished my long angry letter
Dialogue: 1,0:14:52.79,0:14:55.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.79,0:14:55.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are we gonna do?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:55.04,0:14:57.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个送外卖的海绵呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.04,0:14:57.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where is that delivery sponge?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:59.90,0:15:02.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他最好跑去我谷仓里偷看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.90,0:15:02.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He better not've gone a-peeping in my barn
Dialogue: 1,0:15:03.50,0:15:07.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不准碰我美丽的碧拉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.50,0:15:07.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You keep your hands off my beautiful Beulah
Dialogue: 1,0:15:07.12,0:15:09.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我没碰它  只是在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.12,0:15:09.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I wasn't touching her, I was just, uh
Dialogue: 1,0:15:09.22,0:15:10.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,欣赏它的美貌
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.22,0:15:10.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,admiring her beauty
Dialogue: 1,0:15:14.56,0:15:15.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,啊对  我是说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.56,0:15:15.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, I mean
Dialogue: 1,0:15:18.12,0:15:21.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,哪里有点不对劲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.12,0:15:21.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Something ain't right here
Dialogue: 1,0:15:28.99,0:15:31.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,应该是你没错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.99,0:15:31.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I guess it's you
Dialogue: 1,0:15:36.54,0:15:37.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.54,0:15:37.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What the?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:37.45,0:15:40.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们两个城市佬想骗我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.45,0:15:40.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You two city slickers tried to hoodwink me
Dialogue: 1,0:15:41.37,0:15:43.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,碧拉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.37,0:15:43.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where's Beulah?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:43.79,0:15:45.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们不是故意要放碧拉走的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.79,0:15:45.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We didn't mean to let Beulah out
Dialogue: 1,0:15:45.88,0:15:47.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.88,0:15:47.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're sorry
Dialogue: 1,0:15:47.06,0:15:49.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别把我们戳得浑身是洞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.06,0:15:49.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't poke us full of holes
Dialogue: 1,0:15:49.30,0:15:50.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,够了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.30,0:15:50.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Enough
Dialogue: 1,0:15:51.30,0:15:53.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,既然是你们俩丢了它
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.30,0:15:53.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You two lost her
Dialogue: 1,0:15:53.30,0:15:56.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那你们俩就得帮我找到它
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.30,0:15:56.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and you two are gonna help me find her
Dialogue: 1,0:15:56.55,0:15:58.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,75,,一小时后
Dialogue: 1,0:16:06.77,0:16:09.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这办法完全不对
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.77,0:16:09.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're going about this all wrong
Dialogue: 1,0:16:09.74,0:16:12.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,该实行B计划了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.74,0:16:12.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Time to go to plan B
Dialogue: 1,0:16:12.60,0:16:13.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是放弃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.60,0:16:13.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Give up?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:13.64,0:16:15.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对  你个傻子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.64,0:16:15.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, ya idjit
Dialogue: 1,0:16:15.24,0:16:17.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是要设陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.24,0:16:17.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We set traps
Dialogue: 1,0:16:20.30,0:16:22.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,犹如蹄缝间的泥土
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.30,0:16:22.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Like mud through cloven hooves
Dialogue: 1,0:16:22.99,0:16:25.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这就是  猪圈日常
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.99,0:16:25.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,these are the Days of our Sties
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.50,0:16:25.92,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(916,794)}猪圈日常
Dialogue: 1,0:16:27.13,0:16:30.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老头简金斯  我们设好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.13,0:16:30.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, Old Man Jenkins, we've finished our
Dialogue: 1,0:16:30.07,0:16:31.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.07,0:16:31.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:31.47,0:16:34.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对啊  应该是要设陷阱才对的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.47,0:16:34.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we're supposed to be making traps
Dialogue: 1,0:16:34.51,0:16:36.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不是睡午觉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.51,0:16:36.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,not taking naps
Dialogue: 1,0:16:36.22,0:16:39.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这就是陷阱  呆头
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.22,0:16:39.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is the trap, ya mouth-breathers
Dialogue: 1,0:16:39.77,0:16:42.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等到碧拉听到它最爱的肥皂剧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.77,0:16:42.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,When Beulah hears her favorite soap opree
Dialogue: 1,0:16:42.93,0:16:45.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它就会爬上床来看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.93,0:16:45.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,she'll climb in bed to watch it
Dialogue: 1,0:16:45.19,0:16:48.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,爽到动都不会动了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.19,0:16:48.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and be too comfortable to move
Dialogue: 1,0:16:49.14,0:16:51.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等它爽了就抓住它
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.14,0:16:51.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The ol' comfort and catch
Dialogue: 1,0:16:51.11,0:16:53.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我看看你们的陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.11,0:16:53.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now show me your traps
Dialogue: 1,0:16:53.11,0:16:54.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是我的陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.11,0:16:54.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here's my trap
Dialogue: 1,0:16:54.50,0:16:57.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没人能拒绝得了蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.50,0:16:57.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No one can resist Krabby Patties
Dialogue: 1,0:16:57.05,0:16:59.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看看我的陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.05,0:16:59.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look at my trap
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.04,0:17:08.88,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1182,830)}踩上去
Dialogue: 1,0:17:00.04,0:17:02.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等到碧拉踩上去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.04,0:17:02.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,When Beulah steps here
Dialogue: 1,0:17:02.43,0:17:05.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就会触发这根尖刺树枝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.43,0:17:05.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,it triggers this spiked branch
Dialogue: 1,0:17:06.71,0:17:08.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后嘭得一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.71,0:17:08.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and bammo
Dialogue: 1,0:17:09.25,0:17:12.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,晚餐就有猪排吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.25,0:17:12.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's pork chops for dinner
Dialogue: 1,0:17:12.15,0:17:14.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只准设有人道的陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.15,0:17:14.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Humane traps only
Dialogue: 1,0:17:14.34,0:17:17.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是要活捉它  不是要它没命
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.34,0:17:17.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're trying to catch her, not end her life
Dialogue: 1,0:17:17.82,0:17:18.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.82,0:17:18.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fine
Dialogue: 1,0:17:18.93,0:17:20.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可我还是很饿
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.93,0:17:20.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But I'm still hungry
Dialogue: 1,0:17:22.01,0:17:22.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.01,0:17:22.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 1,0:17:22.62,0:17:23.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听到没有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.62,0:17:23.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Did you hear that?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:24.15,0:17:25.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.15,0:17:25.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My trap
Dialogue: 1,0:17:25.01,0:17:26.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.01,0:17:26.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It worked
Dialogue: 1,0:17:26.86,0:17:27.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,捉到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.86,0:17:27.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gotcha
Dialogue: 1,0:17:37.19,0:17:41.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早知道就挑个冷门点的肥皂剧了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.19,0:17:41.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I should have picked a less popular soap opree
Dialogue: 1,0:17:44.50,0:17:45.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是我的陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.50,0:17:45.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's my trap
Dialogue: 1,0:17:50.29,0:17:51.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.29,0:17:51.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:17:51.08,0:17:52.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那些可是给碧拉的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.08,0:17:52.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Those were for Beulah
Dialogue: 1,0:17:52.24,0:17:54.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  我受够了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.24,0:17:54.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Alright, I've had enough
Dialogue: 1,0:17:57.72,0:17:58.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.72,0:17:58.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.93,0:18:04.14,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1606,554)}踩上去
Dialogue: 1,0:18:00.96,0:18:01.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,枕头
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.96,0:18:01.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pillow
Dialogue: 1,0:18:01.87,0:18:02.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.87,0:18:02.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,didn't
Dialogue: 1,0:18:02.54,0:18:03.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,效果
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.54,0:18:03.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,help
Dialogue: 1,0:18:07.91,0:18:09.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.91,0:18:09.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:09.27,0:18:11.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你不知怎的好像比之前更生气了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.27,0:18:11.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Somehow you seem angrier than before
Dialogue: 1,0:18:11.60,0:18:13.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不捉碧拉了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.60,0:18:13.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm done huntin' for Beulah
Dialogue: 1,0:18:13.90,0:18:16.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在我要捉你们两个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.90,0:18:16.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now I'm huntin' you two
Dialogue: 1,0:18:16.20,0:18:17.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,戳得浑身是洞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.20,0:18:17.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,full of holes
Dialogue: 1,0:18:28.93,0:18:32.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我分不清他的邪恶笑声是哪传来的了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.93,0:18:30.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't tell what direction
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.58,0:18:32.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,his evil laughter is coming from
Dialogue: 1,0:18:32.57,0:18:34.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他无处不在
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.57,0:18:34.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's everywhere
Dialogue: 1,0:18:40.55,0:18:42.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这应该能绊倒他们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.55,0:18:42.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This'll trip them up
Dialogue: 1,0:18:51.51,0:18:52.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.51,0:18:52.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:52.50,0:18:53.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们跑哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.50,0:18:53.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where'd they go?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:02.32,0:19:03.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,待在这里应该就安全了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.32,0:19:03.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We should be safe in here
Dialogue: 1,0:19:03.59,0:19:05.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以躲进老头简金斯的胡子里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.59,0:19:05.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,in Old Man Jenkins' beard
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.24,0:19:07.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,75,,几个月后
Dialogue: 1,0:19:07.66,0:19:10.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,胡子里来安家
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.66,0:19:10.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Home, home in a beard
Dialogue: 1,0:19:10.73,0:19:14.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这里胡须胡茬都奇葩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.73,0:19:14.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where the whiskers and stubble are weird
Dialogue: 1,0:19:15.03,0:19:16.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,知道吗  派大星哥们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.03,0:19:16.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You knows what, Brother Patrick?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:18.14,0:19:20.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这简单的生活真平静
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.14,0:19:20.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This simple life is so calmin'
Dialogue: 1,0:19:20.69,0:19:22.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我都忘记我们先前逃什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.69,0:19:22.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I forgot what we was runnin' from
Dialogue: 1,0:19:24.88,0:19:28.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以你觉得我们先前是在逃什么玩意
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.88,0:19:28.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So you reckon we was runnin' from somethin'?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:35.55,0:19:37.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.55,0:19:37.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There it is again
Dialogue: 1,0:19:37.19,0:19:42.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,连着几个月都听见自己胡子里有怪声
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.19,0:19:39.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've been hearing strange sounds
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.82,0:19:42.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,from my whiskers for months now
Dialogue: 1,0:19:42.36,0:19:44.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定是那些混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.36,0:19:44.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I bet it's those punks
Dialogue: 1,0:19:44.87,0:19:46.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,躲在我的胡子里面
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.87,0:19:46.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They're hiding in my beard
Dialogue: 1,0:19:47.79,0:19:49.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要进去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.79,0:19:49.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm goin' in
Dialogue: 1,0:20:00.50,0:20:02.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,到你下了  派大星哥们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.50,0:20:02.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your move, Brother Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:20:04.99,0:20:06.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抽牌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.99,0:20:06.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go fish
Dialogue: 1,0:20:10.37,0:20:12.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抓到你们这群害虫了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.37,0:20:12.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gotcha, varmints
Dialogue: 1,0:20:12.56,0:20:15.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老头简金斯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.56,0:20:15.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Old Man Jenkins
Dialogue: 1,0:20:29.15,0:20:31.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,虽然你们跑得快
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.15,0:20:31.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You two may be fast
Dialogue: 1,0:20:31.36,0:20:34.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但我还有一样杀手锏
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.36,0:20:34.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but I got one more trick up my trousers
Dialogue: 1,0:20:35.92,0:20:38.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要把你们熏出来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.92,0:20:38.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna smoke you out
Dialogue: 1,0:20:44.10,0:20:47.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们迟早都会被我抓到  白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.10,0:20:47.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's just a matter of time, idjits
Dialogue: 1,0:20:54.37,0:20:55.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.37,0:20:55.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh no
Dialogue: 1,0:20:55.06,0:20:56.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,已经穷途末路了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.06,0:20:56.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's the end of the line
Dialogue: 1,0:21:01.69,0:21:04.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们这回逃不掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.69,0:21:04.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're not escaping this time
Dialogue: 1,0:21:05.07,0:21:07.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们大家都逃不掉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.07,0:21:07.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't think any of us are escaping
Dialogue: 1,0:21:07.31,0:21:07.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.31,0:21:07.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look
Dialogue: 1,0:21:15.95,0:21:18.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看  是我的碧拉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.95,0:21:18.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look, it's my Beulah
Dialogue: 1,0:21:32.94,0:21:35.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我着火了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.94,0:21:35.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm on fire
Dialogue: 1,0:21:42.53,0:21:43.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,碧拉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.53,0:21:43.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Beulah?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:48.05,0:21:49.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真的是你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.05,0:21:49.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It is you
Dialogue: 1,0:21:50.00,0:21:51.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你之前上哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.00,0:21:51.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where were you?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:55.42,0:21:57.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我写泄愤信写得太入迷了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.42,0:21:57.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got so caught up in my angry letters
Dialogue: 1,0:21:57.98,0:21:59.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以你就去集市
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.98,0:21:59.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that you went to the fair
Dialogue: 1,0:21:59.41,0:22:01.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,自己参赛了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.41,0:22:01.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and entered the contest on your own?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:01.97,0:22:03.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快看
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.97,0:22:03.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And look
Dialogue: 1,0:22:03.17,0:22:05.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你得了第一名
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.17,0:22:05.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You won first prize
Dialogue: 1,0:22:10.39,0:22:10.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.39,0:22:10.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 1,0:22:11.55,0:22:12.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.55,0:22:12.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here you go
Dialogue: 1,0:22:12.50,0:22:15.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以用这张蟹堡王餐巾纸擦脸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.50,0:22:15.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can dry your face with this Krusty Krab napkin
Dialogue: 1,0:22:17.39,0:22:21.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,原来我的餐巾纸一直都在你身上吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.39,0:22:21.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You had my napkin this whole time?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:21.28,0:22:23.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,肯定是在我另一边口袋
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.28,0:22:23.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Must've been in my other pocket
Dialogue: 1,0:22:24.91,0:22:26.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.91,0:22:26.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Run
